data.description: Sitting high on the hill is this lovely craftsman style home.  Lots of character and charm.  Hardwood floors with primary bedroom on the main floor.  There is an additional room that is currently being used as an office. Cozy up by the gas log fireplace in the living room. Bedrooms 2, 3 and 4 are located on the second floor with a ceiling height slightly under 7 feet.  There appears to be enough room on the second floor to add a second bathroom.  Large lot with a detached garage/shed.  Wrap around porch with a Intex above ground pool that will remain.  Come take a look today.
